00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:01,201 --> 00:00:01,968
Imperial Brother asked you

2
00:00:01,969 --> 00:00:03,713
to change into the clothes
of us Central Plains people.

3
00:00:03,737 --> 00:00:05,038
Yet you disobeyed him.

4
00:00:05,238 --> 00:00:06,272
You're truly a barbarian.

5
00:00:06,473 --> 00:00:07,941
Unable to understand human language.

6
00:00:34,334 --> 00:00:35,334
This time, your father

7
00:00:35,902 --> 00:00:38,104
is taking Concubine Chen
and her son on the autumn hunt.

8
00:00:39,305 --> 00:00:41,408
If you can't take this opportunity

9
00:00:41,708 --> 00:00:44,344
to trample Yin Qi,

10
00:00:44,611 --> 00:00:46,613
you might as well stay in the palace

11
00:00:46,846 --> 00:00:48,648
and save yourself the embarrassment.

12
00:00:51,785 --> 00:00:54,921
Concubine Chen must have used some tricks

13
00:00:55,488 --> 00:00:56,488
to seduce Father.

14
00:00:57,590 --> 00:00:59,726
Father has never taken them
on the autumn hunt before.

15
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:01,094
So.

16
00:01:01,428 --> 00:01:02,494
You must demonstrate

17
00:01:02,495 --> 00:01:04,897
your unparalleled strength as the candidate
for the crown prince

18
00:01:04,898 --> 00:01:06,332
and let your father see it.

19
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:07,733
Otherwise

20
00:01:08,334 --> 00:01:10,336
the little bit of favor he has for you

21
00:01:10,737 --> 00:01:12,939
will be taken away by the other princes.

22
00:01:19,825 --> 00:01:22,828
These things are of no benefit to you.

23
00:01:23,516 --> 00:01:26,186
Don't let me see them again in the future.

24
00:02:05,592 --> 00:02:06,592
Fu'an.

25
00:02:07,393 --> 00:02:08,393
Fu'an.

26
00:02:10,950 --> 00:02:12,552
What orders does Your Highness have?

27
00:02:12,899 --> 00:02:14,059
This tea has lost its flavor.

28
00:02:14,501 --> 00:02:15,735
How did you serve it?

29
00:02:16,536 --> 00:02:17,680
Your Highness, please forgive me

30
00:02:17,704 --> 00:02:19,239
I'll bring you fresh tea right away.

31
00:02:31,517 --> 00:02:34,420
Your Highness, please rest for a while

32
00:02:34,721 --> 00:02:36,990
I've brought you your
favorite persimmon cakes.

33
00:02:37,541 --> 00:02:40,193
The persimmon cakes from the fruit
shop on West street are the sweetest.

34
00:02:40,433 --> 00:02:41,553
You'll definitely like them.

35
00:03:14,794 --> 00:03:15,794
Are they sweet?

36
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:55,500
"Journey With You"

37
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,000
(Episode 4)

38
00:04:59,458 --> 00:05:01,326
The Emperor has ordered General Zhang

39
00:05:01,351 --> 00:05:02,652
to go and guard the border.

40
00:05:03,136 --> 00:05:05,405
He has set off today.

41
00:05:05,772 --> 00:05:10,310
Also, the manager of
Yunshang Pavilion has escaped.

42
00:05:22,021 --> 00:05:24,424
Father has ultimately
followed the advice of Yin Qi.

43
00:05:25,324 --> 00:05:26,591
Recently, Father hasn't just

44
00:05:26,592 --> 00:05:28,527
taken the Imperial City Guard from me

45
00:05:28,528 --> 00:05:29,528
and given it to him

46
00:05:29,762 --> 00:05:32,113
but he has also weakened
Uncle's power considerably.

47
00:05:36,469 --> 00:05:37,469
What else?

48
00:05:38,438 --> 00:05:39,438
Your Highness.

49
00:05:39,605 --> 00:05:41,407
The male concubine Lu wasn't rescued.

50
00:05:43,589 --> 00:05:45,190
Just a male concubine.

51
00:05:45,598 --> 00:05:46,933
If he's gone, he's gone.

52
00:05:46,958 --> 00:05:49,160
Do you need to report
such trivial matters to me?

53
00:05:50,583 --> 00:05:51,583
Understood.

54
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:55,555
As for the owner of Yunshang Pavilion.

55
00:05:55,708 --> 00:05:56,709
Send someone to chase him

56
00:05:58,024 --> 00:05:59,144
and execute him immediately.

57
00:05:59,726 --> 00:06:00,726
Yes.

58
00:06:10,837 --> 00:06:11,837
Yin Qi.

59
00:06:13,072 --> 00:06:14,974
The price you've made me pay...

60
00:06:16,075 --> 00:06:17,877
I'll make you repay it all.

61
00:06:28,454 --> 00:06:29,956
Imperial Brother
really is something else.

62
00:06:31,424 --> 00:06:33,202
He won't even let us
celebrate Mid-Autumn Festival.

63
00:06:33,226 --> 00:06:34,503
If you want to fight, do it quickly.

64
00:06:34,527 --> 00:06:35,847
Don't delay my important matters.

65
00:06:45,104 --> 00:06:46,139
Why hasn't he come yet?

66
00:06:47,073 --> 00:06:48,674
A Qi is never late

67
00:06:49,375 --> 00:06:51,711
especially on such an important day.

68
00:07:05,487 --> 00:07:08,053
I know... I know there's
poison on this knife.

69
00:07:11,297 --> 00:07:12,297
A Qi.

70
00:07:12,465 --> 00:07:13,465
A Qi, are you alright?

71
00:07:13,833 --> 00:07:14,833
A Qi.

72
00:07:15,201 --> 00:07:16,201
Don't scare me.

73
00:07:18,304 --> 00:07:19,304
A Qi.

74
00:07:21,908 --> 00:07:22,908
A Qi.

75
00:07:25,478 --> 00:07:27,180
A Qi, don't scare me, A Qi.

76
00:07:28,815 --> 00:07:29,815
My lord.

77
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,880
You encountered assassins.

78
00:07:31,284 --> 00:07:32,484
Were they sent by Yin Zhou?

79
00:07:32,485 --> 00:07:33,352
My lord, are you hurt?

80
00:07:33,386 --> 00:07:34,620
Go and call Doctor Hu quickly.

81
00:07:35,021 --> 00:07:35,521
Go.

82
00:07:35,788 --> 00:07:36,788
Okay, okay.

83
00:07:48,034 --> 00:07:49,368
Am I going to die again?

84
00:07:50,336 --> 00:07:52,376
I haven't changed the
outcome for Yanzhi and me yet.

85
00:07:53,139 --> 00:07:54,340
I can't die.

86
00:07:58,344 --> 00:07:59,784
I'm afraid before the doctor arrives

87
00:08:00,146 --> 00:08:01,647
the poison in A Qi's body

88
00:08:01,881 --> 00:08:03,449
will take his life.

89
00:08:42,488 --> 00:08:43,488
No.

90
00:08:43,956 --> 00:08:44,956
Yanzhi.

91
00:08:46,292 --> 00:08:47,426
No, Yanzhi.

92
00:08:50,863 --> 00:08:53,432
I don't want you to get
hurt again because of me.

93
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,300
At a time like this

94
00:08:55,601 --> 00:08:56,601
don't say such things.

95
00:08:56,802 --> 00:08:58,002
If I don't suck out the poison

96
00:08:58,271 --> 00:08:59,272
you'll die.

97
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,833
My lord.

98
00:09:31,737 --> 00:09:32,737
My lord.

99
00:09:32,772 --> 00:09:33,506
The doctor is here.

100
00:09:33,673 --> 00:09:34,573
Quickly, examine His Highness.

101
00:09:34,573 --> 00:09:35,573
Doctor Hu, please.

102
00:09:57,263 --> 00:09:58,263
How is he?

103
00:10:00,032 --> 00:10:01,032
My lord.

104
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:04,537
The poison His Highness has is
called One-Day Drunkenness.

105
00:10:04,904 --> 00:10:05,948
It's extremely fast-acting.

106
00:10:05,972 --> 00:10:08,774
It reaches the heart and
lungs within three hours.

107
00:10:09,308 --> 00:10:11,286
Fortunately, His Highness
is blessed with good fortune

108
00:10:11,310 --> 00:10:13,379
and my lord treated him in time.

109
00:10:13,779 --> 00:10:14,779
So.

110
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,880
His life is not in danger?

111
00:10:16,582 --> 00:10:18,584
I'll administer acupuncture to His Highness

112
00:10:18,784 --> 00:10:20,395
to clear the remaining
poison from his body.

113
00:10:20,419 --> 00:10:22,355
It will clear the residual poison from his body

114
00:10:22,488 --> 00:10:23,756
and he should be fine.

115
00:10:24,924 --> 00:10:28,027
But His Highness has
suffered severe injuries

116
00:10:28,628 --> 00:10:30,468
and the poison has
reached his heart and lungs.

117
00:10:31,197 --> 00:10:32,932
He'll need time to recover.

118
00:10:33,265 --> 00:10:35,668
He won't be able to use
martial arts for a while.

119
00:10:37,436 --> 00:10:38,436
Thank you, Doctor Hu.

120
00:10:58,491 --> 00:10:59,491
My lord.

121
00:10:59,825 --> 00:11:00,825
Where are you going?

122
00:11:01,527 --> 00:11:04,072
I know
you want to seek revenge on Yin Zhou.

123
00:11:04,096 --> 00:11:05,031
But think about it

124
00:11:05,064 --> 00:11:06,532
turning against him at this time

125
00:11:06,666 --> 00:11:08,167
will ruin all the plans

126
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,400
we've been making for so long.

127
00:11:09,668 --> 00:11:10,668
My lord.

128
00:11:10,903 --> 00:11:11,903
Think twice.

129
00:11:12,772 --> 00:11:13,572
Don't stop me.

130
00:11:13,773 --> 00:11:14,773
My lord.

131
00:11:15,174 --> 00:11:17,209
I know it's presumptuous of me to say this

132
00:11:17,877 --> 00:11:20,284
but your growing feelings for the Fifth Prince
are becoming harder and harder to control

133
00:11:20,312 --> 00:11:21,623
and will only drag him into this.

134
00:11:21,647 --> 00:11:22,748
Ask yourself honestly.

135
00:11:22,882 --> 00:11:24,116
Is this what you want?

136
00:11:26,886 --> 00:11:28,320
If I hadn't rescued him today

137
00:11:30,022 --> 00:11:31,657
no matter how flawless my plans were,

138
00:11:32,124 --> 00:11:33,124
what good would they do?

139
00:11:37,129 --> 00:11:38,129
Wenjie.

140
00:11:39,031 --> 00:11:40,199
I know what I'm doing.

141
00:11:41,434 --> 00:11:42,535
Take care of A Qi for me.

142
00:11:43,235 --> 00:11:44,235
My Lord,

143
00:11:46,772 --> 00:11:48,007
without my order,

144
00:11:48,307 --> 00:11:50,867
you actually dared to leave the palace
and assassinate a prince?

145
00:11:51,677 --> 00:11:52,911
If any clues are left behind

146
00:11:52,912 --> 00:11:54,747
and Father finds out about me,

147
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:55,780
what will we do?

148
00:11:55,981 --> 00:11:57,783
Yin Qi has been very active recently,

149
00:11:58,184 --> 00:11:59,784
causing Your Highness
to suffer heavy losses.

150
00:11:59,785 --> 00:12:01,220
I must eliminate him

151
00:12:01,654 --> 00:12:03,489
to vent Your Highness's anger.

152
00:12:04,356 --> 00:12:05,516
Whoever opposes Your Highness

153
00:12:06,525 --> 00:12:07,960
is my enemy.

154
00:12:12,631 --> 00:12:16,735
The first rule for someone who has
pledged their life is to obey my orders.

155
00:12:17,903 --> 00:12:19,305
You dare to disobey this order?

156
00:12:20,372 --> 00:12:21,372
It seems

157
00:12:21,507 --> 00:12:22,507
you cannot be kept.

158
00:12:23,008 --> 00:12:25,244
In consideration of your
years of loyalty to me,

159
00:12:25,678 --> 00:12:26,678
I will not kill you.

160
00:12:29,682 --> 00:12:30,682
Your Highness...

161
00:12:30,802 --> 00:12:31,802
Go!

162
00:12:32,518 --> 00:12:33,953
Don't let me see you again.

163
00:12:34,687 --> 00:12:35,687
Your Highness,

164
00:12:35,788 --> 00:12:37,908
This subordinate is willing
to accept any punishment.

165
00:12:38,457 --> 00:12:40,217
Please, Your Highness,
do not drive me away.

166
00:12:40,893 --> 00:12:43,333
This subordinate has fought
on the battlefield for many years

167
00:12:43,729 --> 00:12:45,865
to have the chance to
protect Your Highness.

168
00:12:47,233 --> 00:12:48,300
If you drive me away,

169
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:51,103
it would be better to just kill me.

170
00:12:52,004 --> 00:12:53,004
Your Highness,

171
00:12:53,906 --> 00:12:55,808
this subordinate knows he was wrong.

172
00:12:56,008 --> 00:12:57,768
Please, Your Highness,
do not drive me away.

173
00:13:06,443 --> 00:13:08,520
Oh, Young Master,

174
00:13:08,854 --> 00:13:10,294
you've come at an inconvenient time.

175
00:13:10,523 --> 00:13:12,024
Your Highness has given orders

176
00:13:12,324 --> 00:13:14,404
to close the doors and not
receive any guests today.

177
00:13:14,727 --> 00:13:16,428
Please, Young Master, go back.

178
00:13:18,664 --> 00:13:19,732
I want to see Yin Zhou.

179
00:13:19,932 --> 00:13:21,400
Didn't Young Master hear?

180
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,520
Your Highness is not
receiving any guests today.

181
00:13:24,770 --> 00:13:25,770
Pei Yanzhi,

182
00:13:26,272 --> 00:13:27,272
why is he here?

183
00:13:28,741 --> 00:13:30,609
It's all for his Fifth Prince.

184
00:13:32,578 --> 00:13:33,579
Go hide in the study.

185
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:35,740
If you act on your own again,

186
00:13:36,315 --> 00:13:37,850
don't blame me for being ruthless.

187
00:13:38,751 --> 00:13:39,751
Yes, sir.

188
00:13:44,309 --> 00:13:44,977
Fu'an,

189
00:13:45,171 --> 00:13:46,171
let him in.

190
00:14:08,748 --> 00:14:09,748
Do you know

191
00:14:11,083 --> 00:14:13,461
that just by forcing your way
into Mingde Palace with a blade,

192
00:14:13,486 --> 00:14:15,889
I can have your family
executed for your crime?

193
00:14:16,055 --> 00:14:17,556
Why did you go back on your word

194
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:19,070
and send someone to assassinate A Qi?

195
00:14:20,726 --> 00:14:22,261
How can I explain something.

196
00:14:23,028 --> 00:14:24,630
I have never done?

197
00:14:26,098 --> 00:14:28,400
You've tried every means
to drive A Qi to the border,

198
00:14:28,834 --> 00:14:29,468
and when that failed,

199
00:14:29,469 --> 00:14:30,869
you developed murderous intentions,

200
00:14:31,070 --> 00:14:32,972
wanting to eliminate A Qi completely.

201
00:14:39,245 --> 00:14:40,479
If you have no sincerity,

202
00:14:42,314 --> 00:14:43,992
it seems our alliance
does not need to continue.

203
00:14:44,016 --> 00:14:45,484
If you dare to give up halfway,

204
00:14:46,218 --> 00:14:47,486
I will show you.

205
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:49,655
Yin Qi's fate

206
00:14:50,623 --> 00:14:52,491
will be a hundred times worse than this.

207
00:14:53,158 --> 00:14:55,160
Your Highness actually
has an alliance with him?

208
00:14:55,661 --> 00:14:57,096
I shouldn't have been so reckless.

209
00:14:57,863 --> 00:14:59,583
I actually made Your Highness cover for me.

210
00:15:00,032 --> 00:15:00,466
Next time,

211
00:15:00,899 --> 00:15:01,899
I must not fail.

212
00:15:04,036 --> 00:15:05,036
Other than you,

213
00:15:05,904 --> 00:15:07,907
who else wants to kill A Qi?

214
00:15:08,774 --> 00:15:09,774
Don't forget

215
00:15:10,776 --> 00:15:12,243
that Yin Qi caused Yunshang Pavilion

216
00:15:12,244 --> 00:15:14,680
to be emptied overnight.

217
00:15:16,982 --> 00:15:17,982
Do you think

218
00:15:18,851 --> 00:15:20,319
they might

219
00:15:21,921 --> 00:15:23,455
come back to take revenge on Yin Qi?

220
00:15:28,927 --> 00:15:30,462
Just think about it,

221
00:15:31,196 --> 00:15:33,098
if I am determined

222
00:15:33,866 --> 00:15:37,201
to assassinate Yin Qi when he is
alone outside the palace,

223
00:15:38,237 --> 00:15:40,039
how could it possibly fail?

224
00:15:45,044 --> 00:15:47,646
I came here today to tell Your Highness.

225
00:15:48,447 --> 00:15:49,447
A Qi

226
00:15:50,082 --> 00:15:51,450
is my bottom line.

227
00:15:54,019 --> 00:15:55,179
Your Highness should be clear

228
00:15:55,708 --> 00:15:57,516
that you and I are on the same boat.

229
00:15:58,424 --> 00:15:59,858
If I overturn this boat,

230
00:16:00,726 --> 00:16:01,726
Your Highness

231
00:16:02,728 --> 00:16:03,808
will be in danger yourself.

232
00:16:12,071 --> 00:16:14,191
Why did Your Highness
become an ally with Pei Yanzhi?

233
00:16:16,709 --> 00:16:18,544
It's because of you useless people.

234
00:16:18,978 --> 00:16:21,246
If you could help me solve my problems,

235
00:16:21,313 --> 00:16:23,473
would I still need to form
an alliance with a hostage?

236
00:16:27,019 --> 00:16:28,287
This subordinate is useless.

237
00:16:29,621 --> 00:16:30,981
Please, Your Highness, forgive me.

238
00:16:39,965 --> 00:16:40,965
Does it hurt?

239
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:49,174
This subordinate never thought
Your Highness would defend me.

240
00:16:50,309 --> 00:16:51,309
Just now,

241
00:16:52,044 --> 00:16:53,845
this subordinate saw Your
Highness come to my rescue.

242
00:16:53,846 --> 00:16:55,080
Does it also mean...

243
00:16:56,982 --> 00:16:58,217
that in Your Highness's heart,

244
00:16:59,651 --> 00:17:00,986
there is a trace of care for me?

245
00:17:06,392 --> 00:17:07,712
This subordinate has overstepped.

246
00:17:08,227 --> 00:17:09,587
Please, Your Highness, forgive me.

247
00:17:11,263 --> 00:17:13,265
What is Pei Yanzhi worth?

248
00:17:13,999 --> 00:17:16,635
He actually wants to hold
my people accountable.

249
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:19,070
In this world,

250
00:17:20,072 --> 00:17:21,073
no one can punish you

251
00:17:22,408 --> 00:17:23,909
except me.

252
00:17:28,714 --> 00:17:29,782
You're right.

253
00:17:30,783 --> 00:17:32,785
If even you are not by my side,

254
00:17:33,685 --> 00:17:35,020
in this vast imperial city,

255
00:17:36,422 --> 00:17:40,092
who else can understand my feelings?

256
00:17:42,694 --> 00:17:44,574
Just being able to stay
by Your Highness's side

257
00:17:45,831 --> 00:17:46,932
is a great favor

258
00:17:49,101 --> 00:17:50,502
for this subordinate.

259
00:18:32,311 --> 00:18:33,311
Where am I?

260
00:18:35,581 --> 00:18:38,407
Your Highness was injured by
an assassin and was poisoned.

261
00:18:39,218 --> 00:18:41,818
My lord was worried that
you wouldn't make it back to the palace,

262
00:18:42,121 --> 00:18:43,755
so he brought you to Piaoxiang Pavilion.

263
00:18:58,604 --> 00:18:59,604
Where's Yanzhi?

264
00:19:00,239 --> 00:19:01,240
Where is he?

265
00:19:01,974 --> 00:19:04,109
Your Highness, do you know

266
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:05,811
that your repeated investigations

267
00:19:05,844 --> 00:19:07,246
into what my lord has done

268
00:19:07,513 --> 00:19:09,248
will only bring him endless trouble?

269
00:19:16,688 --> 00:19:19,625
Can you do something about you and
your lord's stubborness and bad temper?

270
00:19:20,025 --> 00:19:21,058
If I don't stop Yanzhi,

271
00:19:21,059 --> 00:19:22,661
I'll be pushing him to his doom.

272
00:19:23,929 --> 00:19:26,331
Do you have to see his corpse

273
00:19:26,665 --> 00:19:27,766
before you believe me?

274
00:19:29,401 --> 00:19:30,635
Your Highness has grown up in the palace,

275
00:19:30,636 --> 00:19:31,904
living a life of luxury.

276
00:19:32,204 --> 00:19:34,071
How can you understand my lord's situation?

277
00:19:34,673 --> 00:19:36,108
He has worked tirelessly for you,

278
00:19:36,441 --> 00:19:37,441
and what do you do?

279
00:19:37,676 --> 00:19:39,111
Instead of being grateful to him,

280
00:19:39,678 --> 00:19:41,079
you come here and meddle.

281
00:19:42,814 --> 00:19:44,349
If you really care about your lord,

282
00:19:44,850 --> 00:19:45,850
then tell me

283
00:19:46,111 --> 00:19:47,446
what he is planning.

284
00:19:50,923 --> 00:19:51,923
My lord...!

285
00:19:52,991 --> 00:19:53,991
Give us the room.

286
00:20:06,805 --> 00:20:07,925
Why did you come to save me?

287
00:20:08,607 --> 00:20:09,942
How did you leave the room?

288
00:20:11,577 --> 00:20:13,878
Is this how you talk
to the person who saved you?

289
00:20:16,615 --> 00:20:18,217
Did Heshu let you out?

290
00:20:18,817 --> 00:20:19,817
Besides her,

291
00:20:20,018 --> 00:20:21,286
no one else has the courage.

292
00:20:22,187 --> 00:20:23,288
Even if you saved me,

293
00:20:23,922 --> 00:20:24,957
I won't let you

294
00:20:24,990 --> 00:20:26,024
carry out your plan.

295
00:20:26,049 --> 00:20:27,049
A Qi,

296
00:20:27,626 --> 00:20:28,727
I just don't understand

297
00:20:29,228 --> 00:20:30,262
why do you always think

298
00:20:31,096 --> 00:20:32,464
that I will definitely fail?

299
00:20:41,506 --> 00:20:42,506
Brother,

300
00:20:42,874 --> 00:20:43,874
Brother,

301
00:20:44,009 --> 00:20:45,009
Brother,

302
00:20:45,577 --> 00:20:47,111
I heard from Yanzhi that you were injured.

303
00:20:47,112 --> 00:20:47,713
I was so worried.

304
00:20:48,113 --> 00:20:49,281
Let me see where you're hurt.

305
00:20:49,481 --> 00:20:50,782
If you keep shouting like this,

306
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,250
the whole palace

307
00:20:52,417 --> 00:20:53,497
will know that I'm injured.

308
00:20:55,621 --> 00:20:56,421
Don't worry,

309
00:20:56,421 --> 00:20:57,421
your brother is fine.

310
00:21:00,292 --> 00:21:02,370
Fortunately, the poison in my body
has been neutralized.

311
00:21:02,394 --> 00:21:04,154
But it has still injured
your internal organs.

312
00:21:04,496 --> 00:21:06,016
You still need to rest and recuperate.

313
00:21:07,552 --> 00:21:09,272
This minister will go get the medicine now.

314
00:21:13,105 --> 00:21:14,105
Thank you, Young Master.

315
00:21:14,406 --> 00:21:17,446
Please come with this official to the
Imperial Hospital to get the medicine.

316
00:21:27,786 --> 00:21:29,086
The Fifth Prince is by your side,

317
00:21:29,087 --> 00:21:30,288
living in fear every day,

318
00:21:30,789 --> 00:21:32,190
either getting injured or poisoned.

319
00:21:32,491 --> 00:21:33,825
How are you taking care of him?

320
00:21:37,829 --> 00:21:40,065
I thought you would
protect and take care of him,

321
00:21:40,666 --> 00:21:43,502
but it turns out you're just a jinx.

322
00:21:44,236 --> 00:21:45,503
It's all because of you

323
00:21:45,504 --> 00:21:47,105
that he almost died.

324
00:21:47,806 --> 00:21:50,342
People like you don't deserve
to stay by his side.

325
00:21:51,843 --> 00:21:55,960
Whether I deserve to stay by his
side or not is not up to you to decide.

326
00:21:57,015 --> 00:21:58,684
The matters between A Qi and me

327
00:21:59,284 --> 00:22:00,324
are none of your business.

328
00:22:10,462 --> 00:22:11,462
So,

329
00:22:11,663 --> 00:22:13,532
last night, you didn't
clear things up at all.

330
00:22:13,965 --> 00:22:14,965
And you got stabbed.

331
00:22:20,458 --> 00:22:22,103
Yanzhi has always been
like this since he was a child.

332
00:22:22,441 --> 00:22:24,042
If he doesn't want to say something,

333
00:22:24,309 --> 00:22:25,309
no one can force him.

334
00:22:26,578 --> 00:22:27,578
It seems

335
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:29,948
we need to use some special methods

336
00:22:30,449 --> 00:22:31,583
to pry his mouth open.

337
00:22:35,987 --> 00:22:36,987
Last night,

338
00:22:37,388 --> 00:22:37,989
was it you

339
00:22:38,124 --> 00:22:39,524
who secretly let Yanzhi out?

340
00:22:40,225 --> 00:22:41,426
So what if it was?

341
00:22:42,294 --> 00:22:43,428
If I hadn't been clever

342
00:22:43,462 --> 00:22:44,863
and let Yanzhi out,

343
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:46,331
you might have already...

344
00:22:47,858 --> 00:22:48,459
Anyway,

345
00:22:48,667 --> 00:22:50,368
I can be considered your half-savior.

346
00:22:50,502 --> 00:22:51,702
If you don't appreciate me, that's fine,

347
00:22:51,703 --> 00:22:52,703
but hitting me...?

348
00:22:54,272 --> 00:22:56,208
I was afraid that Yanzhi
would leave the room

349
00:22:57,342 --> 00:22:59,844
and go work for Su He and Yin Zhou again.

350
00:23:00,612 --> 00:23:01,612
What if

351
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:03,815
one day, everything is exposed?

352
00:23:07,085 --> 00:23:08,830
Today, when you hadn't
returned to the palace yet,

353
00:23:08,854 --> 00:23:10,454
Yanzhi caused a commotion in Mingde Palace

354
00:23:10,455 --> 00:23:11,890
and turned everything upside down.

355
00:23:12,457 --> 00:23:14,359
It might have been

356
00:23:14,426 --> 00:23:16,127
to seek revenge for your
assassination last night

357
00:23:16,128 --> 00:23:17,362
by going after Yin Zhou.

358
00:23:18,497 --> 00:23:19,497
You're saying...

359
00:23:20,031 --> 00:23:22,734
Yanzhi caused a commotion in Mingde Palace?

360
00:23:24,002 --> 00:23:25,002
What?

361
00:23:25,103 --> 00:23:27,572
Do you know how important
you are to Yanzhi now?

362
00:23:27,873 --> 00:23:29,040
You must be overjoyed.

363
00:23:31,376 --> 00:23:32,416
Don't be so disrespectful.

364
00:23:39,477 --> 00:23:41,971
Your growing feelings for the Fifth
Prince will only drag him into this,

365
00:23:42,454 --> 00:23:43,734
and make you lose your judgment.

366
00:23:43,855 --> 00:23:44,895
Don't be so disrespectful.

367
00:23:45,223 --> 00:23:45,891
People like you

368
00:23:46,091 --> 00:23:47,731
simply don't deserve to stay by his side.

369
00:23:48,527 --> 00:23:49,527
They were right.

370
00:23:50,429 --> 00:23:51,429
No matter what,

371
00:23:51,730 --> 00:23:53,932
A Qi must not be dragged
into this matter again.

372
00:23:55,367 --> 00:23:56,527
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

373
00:23:56,635 --> 00:23:57,635
Why did you come out?

374
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:00,238
Doctor Bai said I'm fine.

375
00:24:07,686 --> 00:24:08,686
Today...

376
00:24:08,947 --> 00:24:10,027
did you go to Mingde Palace

377
00:24:10,415 --> 00:24:11,716
and make a scene with Yinzhou?

378
00:24:13,063 --> 00:24:14,823
Even if I level Mingde
Palace to the ground,

379
00:24:14,933 --> 00:24:17,621
it still can't make up for
the harm Yinzhou has done to you.

380
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:21,541
You said you wanted to
clear away all obstacles for me.

381
00:24:22,494 --> 00:24:23,695
I know you care about me.

382
00:24:24,663 --> 00:24:25,663
But what I want

383
00:24:26,298 --> 00:24:28,018
is not constant concealment and protection.

384
00:24:28,467 --> 00:24:29,467
Moreover

385
00:24:29,634 --> 00:24:30,634
your so-called protection

386
00:24:31,303 --> 00:24:34,039
is very likely to become a
blade that drives us apart.

387
00:24:35,907 --> 00:24:36,907
That day...

388
00:24:37,268 --> 00:24:38,268
you...

389
00:24:44,316 --> 00:24:45,316
Your Highness.

390
00:24:45,684 --> 00:24:47,084
This matter goes against the rules.

391
00:24:48,272 --> 00:24:50,312
Have you not done things
that go against the rules?

392
00:24:50,522 --> 00:24:53,124
You risked your life to secretly
escort my mother back to Jiangnan.

393
00:24:53,859 --> 00:24:56,261
Do you dare to say
it wasn't for me?

394
00:24:57,195 --> 00:24:58,806
Imperial Concubine Chen
treated me extremely well

395
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:01,032
I sent her back to Jiangnan
to repay her kindness.

396
00:25:03,034 --> 00:25:04,034
Your Highness.

397
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:06,450
You'd better not think too much.

398
00:25:06,505 --> 00:25:07,539
What about today?

399
00:25:08,106 --> 00:25:09,106
Today.

400
00:25:09,441 --> 00:25:10,842
Why did you go after Yinzhou?

401
00:25:11,810 --> 00:25:13,545
If you really follow the rules so strictly

402
00:25:14,913 --> 00:25:15,981
why did you allow yourself

403
00:25:18,116 --> 00:25:19,317
to fall in love with me?

404
00:25:20,118 --> 00:25:20,652
I didn't.

405
00:25:20,685 --> 00:25:21,685
Your Highness.

406
00:25:26,491 --> 00:25:27,731
Your Highness, please
take good care of yourself.

407
00:25:27,756 --> 00:25:31,571
I won't come to Yunhe Palace for a while if
there's nothing important during this period.

408
00:25:48,046 --> 00:25:49,781
Your Highness should rest now.

409
00:25:50,448 --> 00:25:51,716
The wound is a bit deep.

410
00:25:52,183 --> 00:25:53,423
It will take some time to heal.

411
00:25:55,673 --> 00:25:58,980
This little wound
means nothing to me.

412
00:26:02,627 --> 00:26:03,627
Your Highness

413
00:26:04,329 --> 00:26:06,998
I've had something in
my heart for a long time.

414
00:26:10,368 --> 00:26:11,703
If Your Highness turns back now

415
00:26:12,176 --> 00:26:13,654
and stays away from all these disputes

416
00:26:13,972 --> 00:26:16,007
you can still be a
carefree prince for life.

417
00:26:17,475 --> 00:26:20,345
Am I so useless in your eyes
that you think in such a way?

418
00:26:20,779 --> 00:26:22,213
That's not what I mean.

419
00:26:22,915 --> 00:26:25,293
I'm willing to take care of Your Highness
for the rest of my life.

420
00:26:25,450 --> 00:26:27,170
Even if the person in Your Highness's heart

421
00:26:27,485 --> 00:26:28,620
is not me.

422
00:26:31,122 --> 00:26:32,122
But

423
00:26:32,324 --> 00:26:33,391
given time,

424
00:26:34,593 --> 00:26:36,294
Your Highness might forget the one

425
00:26:37,095 --> 00:26:38,129
who hurt you.

426
00:26:41,766 --> 00:26:42,766
Nanxing.

427
00:26:43,668 --> 00:26:44,788
Thank you for your kindness.

428
00:26:46,304 --> 00:26:47,304
But

429
00:26:48,647 --> 00:26:49,915
to make me forget Yanzhi...

430
00:26:50,809 --> 00:26:51,809
I'm afraid...

431
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,577
I cannot.

432
00:26:59,477 --> 00:27:01,112
I thought since we grew up together...

433
00:27:02,020 --> 00:27:05,190
your Highness would
have a place for me in your heart.

434
00:27:10,462 --> 00:27:11,462
Your Highness.

435
00:27:12,063 --> 00:27:13,841
Are you really so deeply in
love with the young master

436
00:27:13,865 --> 00:27:15,233
that you feel this way?

437
00:27:19,704 --> 00:27:20,704
I only know

438
00:27:21,773 --> 00:27:23,174
at the moment I was hurt

439
00:27:25,043 --> 00:27:26,878
he was the one I most wanted to see.

440
00:27:31,082 --> 00:27:32,117
However

441
00:27:33,918 --> 00:27:35,320
it's all just my wishful thinking.

442
00:27:36,254 --> 00:27:37,254
Yanzhi only regards me

443
00:27:37,989 --> 00:27:39,457
as a brother.

444
00:27:42,661 --> 00:27:45,296
Although I don't like the young noble

445
00:27:46,498 --> 00:27:47,498
but in this matter.

446
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:50,020
I still have to speak
up for the young noble.

447
00:27:51,469 --> 00:27:53,829
If your Highness thinks the young
noble doesn't care about you,

448
00:27:54,039 --> 00:27:55,507
then you're really wronging him.

449
00:27:55,907 --> 00:27:57,142
As bystanders

450
00:27:57,675 --> 00:27:59,110
we can see clearly

451
00:27:59,644 --> 00:28:02,480
what kind of feelings the
young noble has for you.

452
00:28:11,089 --> 00:28:12,290
But sometimes

453
00:28:13,992 --> 00:28:15,827
even I can't see it clearly myself.

454
00:28:19,264 --> 00:28:21,533
Since the young noble cares
so much about Your Highness

455
00:28:21,766 --> 00:28:23,367
but doesn't want Your Highness

456
00:28:23,368 --> 00:28:25,003
to realize this care

457
00:28:26,638 --> 00:28:29,441
that means in the young noble's view,

458
00:28:29,841 --> 00:28:30,842
this affection

459
00:28:32,043 --> 00:28:33,778
might bring danger to Your Highness.

460
00:28:46,391 --> 00:28:48,460
Yanzhi fought with Yinzhou for me.

461
00:28:48,893 --> 00:28:50,128
It shows that he hasn't

462
00:28:50,495 --> 00:28:51,830
completely betrayed the Emperor

463
00:28:52,330 --> 00:28:53,631
and become Yin Zhou's ally.

464
00:28:54,766 --> 00:28:56,301
I must do everything in my power

465
00:28:56,468 --> 00:28:57,736
to keep him by my side.

466
00:28:58,403 --> 00:28:59,403
In this way

467
00:28:59,637 --> 00:29:01,339
he won't go astray.

468
00:29:07,245 --> 00:29:07,979
Heshu

469
00:29:08,012 --> 00:29:10,148
I just heard from the servants
that A Qi is missing.

470
00:29:10,248 --> 00:29:10,849
What does that mean?

471
00:29:10,850 --> 00:29:11,970
What do they mean by missing?

472
00:29:12,283 --> 00:29:13,283
At noon today

473
00:29:13,418 --> 00:29:14,886
a guard saw him leave the palace

474
00:29:15,086 --> 00:29:16,488
but he hasn't come back yet.

475
00:29:17,122 --> 00:29:18,666
If he can't return to the
palace before curfew

476
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:20,334
it will be trouble if
the Emperor finds out.

477
00:29:20,358 --> 00:29:21,192
Brother Yanzhi.

478
00:29:21,193 --> 00:29:22,794
Do you know where my brother would go?

479
00:29:24,429 --> 00:29:24,829
I think.

480
00:29:25,296 --> 00:29:26,297
I can find him.

481
00:29:51,422 --> 00:29:52,662
I hope my journey goes smoothly

482
00:29:52,824 --> 00:29:54,259
to protect Yanzhi's family and clan

483
00:29:55,193 --> 00:29:57,629
and to resolve the border
disputes for our country.

484
00:30:00,632 --> 00:30:01,065
Yanzhi.

485
00:30:01,332 --> 00:30:02,332
What wish did you make?

486
00:30:05,503 --> 00:30:06,503
A Qi.

487
00:30:07,105 --> 00:30:08,306
I hope that in this life

488
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,240
you will be safe, happy

489
00:30:11,442 --> 00:30:12,442
free and fearless.

490
00:30:36,434 --> 00:30:37,434
Yanzhi.

491
00:30:38,369 --> 00:30:40,171
When you made this wish in your past life,

492
00:30:40,905 --> 00:30:42,140
were you sincere?

493
00:30:57,455 --> 00:30:58,575
How did you know I was here?

494
00:31:00,925 --> 00:31:01,925
You put so much effort

495
00:31:02,794 --> 00:31:04,634
into making the sky
lantern for Concubine Chen

496
00:31:05,463 --> 00:31:06,664
you must want her to see it.

497
00:31:08,766 --> 00:31:10,268
We fly sky lanterns every year.

498
00:31:11,269 --> 00:31:12,469
Especially in the first year
after my mother passed away,

499
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:15,673
we must fly them,
otherwise she would worry.

500
00:31:37,695 --> 00:31:38,695
Do you think

501
00:31:39,898 --> 00:31:41,332
my mother can see this lantern?

502
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:49,908
This sky lantern

503
00:31:52,677 --> 00:31:54,357
is the letter you wrote to Concubine Chen.

504
00:31:57,782 --> 00:31:58,782
She will receive it.

505
00:32:02,013 --> 00:32:03,013
Yanzhi.

506
00:32:05,190 --> 00:32:07,992
I want to hear an
answer from you.

507
00:32:10,134 --> 00:32:12,803
How do you feel about me?

508
00:32:16,153 --> 00:32:17,153
A Qi.

509
00:32:17,368 --> 00:32:18,968
You're confused because of your illness.

510
00:32:19,570 --> 00:32:20,872
Why are you talking nonsense?

511
00:32:22,707 --> 00:32:24,509
It's getting late.

512
00:32:24,976 --> 00:32:25,877
Let's hurry back to the palace.

513
00:32:25,878 --> 00:32:27,412
When will you finally admit

514
00:32:29,380 --> 00:32:30,448
your feelings for me?

515
00:32:34,485 --> 00:32:35,485
A Qi.

516
00:32:36,321 --> 00:32:37,761
What nonsense are you talking about?

517
00:32:38,323 --> 00:32:39,323
We...

518
00:32:40,002 --> 00:32:41,059
are just good brothers.

519
00:32:41,659 --> 00:32:43,299
There's no such thing as like or dislike.

520
00:32:43,428 --> 00:32:43,795
You...

521
00:32:43,795 --> 00:32:44,795
I once asked you

522
00:32:45,863 --> 00:32:47,265
why you treated me so well.

523
00:32:48,666 --> 00:32:50,601
You said that's how brothers should be.

524
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:53,504
I asked you again

525
00:32:54,472 --> 00:32:56,341
why you risked your life to help me.

526
00:32:58,076 --> 00:33:00,144
You said you had to
repay my mother's kindness.

527
00:33:03,047 --> 00:33:04,047
You always talk about

528
00:33:04,916 --> 00:33:07,585
righteousness, morality, loyalty,
and responsibility towards me.

529
00:33:09,787 --> 00:33:11,022
Is there nothing else?

530
00:33:53,431 --> 00:33:54,551
Do you still dare to say now

531
00:33:55,299 --> 00:33:56,601
that we're just brothers?

532
00:34:05,076 --> 00:34:06,344
Your hands are so cold.

533
00:34:11,182 --> 00:34:12,182
Treating me like this.

534
00:34:13,050 --> 00:34:14,050
Is it really worth it?

535
00:34:24,929 --> 00:34:25,929
Your Highness.

536
00:34:26,297 --> 00:34:27,297
If you do this,

537
00:34:27,498 --> 00:34:29,934
the Crown Prince
will surely cause trouble for you.

538
00:34:31,202 --> 00:34:33,237
Imperial Brother is always
good at using this trick.

539
00:34:34,038 --> 00:34:35,540
I'm just using his own methods

540
00:34:35,573 --> 00:34:36,774
to deal with him.

541
00:34:37,308 --> 00:34:38,409
Let him make his move.

542
00:34:38,709 --> 00:34:40,745
Only then can I find his flaws.

543
00:34:43,381 --> 00:34:44,982
We know what to do.

544
00:34:52,290 --> 00:34:53,867
You can go and attend
to your business first.

545
00:34:53,891 --> 00:34:55,051
We shall take our leave.

546
00:34:57,028 --> 00:34:58,188
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

547
00:34:58,396 --> 00:34:59,476
Why did you come out again?

548
00:35:04,469 --> 00:35:05,536
Because I know

549
00:35:06,103 --> 00:35:07,505
you'll come to bring me a cloak.

550
